    <title>Speech to Text Platform</title>


    <h1>Speech to Text Platform</h1>
    <p>This platform provides advanced speech recognition capabilities, allowing users to convert spoken language into written text efficiently and accurately.</p>
    <button id="startButton">Start Recording</button>
    <button id="stopButton" disabled="">Stop Recording</button>
    <p id="status">Status: Inactive</p>
    
    <h2>Playback</h2>
    <audio id="audioElement" controls=""></audio>
    <a id="downloadLink" style="display: none;">Download Audio</a>
